  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Members did not act according to the decision taken by the parties - Maithiri",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Maithripala Sirisena, the former President and Chairman of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party, said that the results of the election show that the members did not take decisions regarding the decisions taken by the parties regarding the election of the new President.",
        "The President said this while addressing the media at the Parliament premises after the completion of the poll.",
        "The election of the President took place today in a parliamentary democratic manner.. We should accept the election results accordingly.",
        "We should think about the future and strengthen our party. Now Parliament is on one side and the people are on the other. This is the truth. Because this is not the result people expected.",
        "Also, it seems that not only our party, but all the parties have not taken the decisions of the members regarding the decisions taken by the party in the matter of new president election. We can realize it through the election results.",
        "At the same time, in the crisis that the country is currently facing, we are ready to provide necessary cooperation to any person for the country, he said"
      ],
